# output file name
Output fish.gif

# sizing
Set Width 830
Set Height 467
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "GitHub Dark"

# font
Set FontFamily "CaskaydiaCove Nerd Font"
Set FontSize 16

# setup
Hide
Type fish
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type clear
Enter
Sleep 100ms
Show

# intro
Type "# fish allows you to customize your shell with functions"
Enter
Sleep 100ms

# pypi.fish demo
Type "# for example, pypi.fish let's you search PyPI"
Enter
Sleep 100ms

Type "pypi -h"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type clear
Enter
Sleep 100ms

